        .container { width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; }
        h2 { color: #0073e6; }
        p { font-size: 16px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</h2>
        <p>We hope you're doing well! Just a reminder that your subscription started on <b><%= startDate %></b> and is approaching its renewal time.</p>
        <p>Please ensure your payment details are up to date to continue enjoying our services.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing us!</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><b>EaseTruck</b></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
